sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    actor User as Patient
    participant UI as Assessment Interface
    participant AI as AI Engine (Risk Analyzer)
    participant DB as SQL Server Database
    participant Support as Specialist / Crisis Hotline

    User->>UI: Selects "Red Flag" Answer (Weight 50)
    
    UI->>AI: Instant Transmission of Critical Score
    
    activate AI
    Note over AI: Logic Check: Score >= 50
    AI->>AI: Terminate Assessment Flow
    
    par Mitigation Actions
        AI->>DB: Insert Emergency Log (Encrypted)
        Note right of DB: High Privacy via SQL Encryption
        AI->>Support: Trigger Urgent Alert to Specialist
    end

    AI-->>UI: Return Emergency Protocol Template
    deactivate AI

    UI-->>User: Display Mandatory Emergency Disclaimer
    UI->>User: Show "Contact Specialist" & "Local Hotline" Links
    
    opt User seeks immediate help
        User->>UI: Click "Call Hotline"
        UI->>Support: Direct Secure Link Established
    end